{"type": "article", "id": 24604, "title": "郁金香户外伞", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-29T06:59:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021259468UhSul6vqPYD9wRZ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这把用于户外的伞是一个倒三角，像一个打开的郁金香，因为打开的面积很大且接近水平，它依然有挡雨和遮阳的功能，也带有一些未来感。雨水是顺着中间的柱子往地下流的，有助于集中排水。它是用铝结构和有一定防水效果的面料制成，可承担 60 km/h 的风速和 350 mm 水压。可以选择 11 种颜色来适应各种气氛，<a href=\"https://www.mdt-tex.com/en/products/tulip-umbrella/type-e/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125943Ax29G0s18cCgbLy7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125944YNp2i6GRVQ3Kej9f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76433121\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"dragged\" style=\"height: 242px; width: 375px; left: 452px; top: 745px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125944GcuwyaJnzThUbf4i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64550781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125945T5f3GcLbUwXoK21v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125945AZGJ9qQwdhme6iLc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}